query:
SELECT /* batch.PostgresServersRepository.find_server_config */
                   s.config_name 
                 , NULL          AS private_key
                 , s.private_ip  AS address
                 , 51280         AS "port!"
              FROM servers s
        INNER JOIN vpns v
                ON s.vpn_id = s.vpn_id 
             WHERE 1=1
               AND s.vpn_id = $1
               AND NOT s.is_deleted 
               AND NOT v.is_deleted 
        ;
